Proud grandmother, Shauwn Mkhize, took to Instagram to announce and celebrate the birth of yet another grandchild, baby Miaandy, on Tuesday. Mkhize, businesswoman and reality TV star, threw a lavish party to celebrate her granddaughter’s arrival to their home. MaMkhize’s son, Andile Mpisane, and his wife Tamia Mpisane welcomed their bundle of joy to the world on Sunday morning. The proud granny posted on Instagram how excited she was to welcome the new member of the family. “Welcome Home Baby Royal AM. You are loved beyond measure, and we are all excited to watch you grow. “You have extended our family and our hearts are full. Thank you for being our ray of sunshine and beacon of hope,” she wrote. “We love you and we will always stand by your side,” Mkhize added. Social media users took to her comment section to share their thoughts on the baby’s unusual name Miaandy, until one user pointed out that her name is actually a mash-up of Tamia and Andile’s names, “Ta-mia and Andi-le, Miaandy.”